      <chapter id="774">
        <pagenum>2</pagenum>
        <subchapter>0</subchapter>
        <title>Activity: Depicting the relationships and influences of the six self-determination factors</title>
        <content>&lt;h1 class="Subhead"&gt;Activity: Depicting the relationships and influences of the six &lt;span class="nolink"&gt;self-determination&lt;/span&gt; factors&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please take a moment to consider what you have learned about the six factors. If you were asked to create a visual model or describe an analogy of how these six factors support the process of becoming self-determined, what would it look like/be?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;How might you depict ways in which the six factors that influence &lt;span class="nolink"&gt;self-determination&lt;/span&gt; relate to and influence one another?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When you have finished your reflections, click the &lt;b&gt;forward arrow&lt;/b&gt; to proceed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/No_Tree_graphic_CC.jpg" width="550" height="449" alt="Header: Self Determination Model. Six factors of self-determination: Gain self-awareness; Reflect and readjust; Plan; Be proactive; Learn to value oneself; and Environment." /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
