      <chapter id="778">
        <pagenum>6</pagenum>
        <subchapter>0</subchapter>
        <title>Orange tree represents being proactive</title>
        <content>&lt;h1 class="Subhead"&gt;Orange tree represents &lt;span class="nolink"&gt;being proactiv&lt;/span&gt;e&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="nolink"&gt;Being proactive&lt;/span&gt; is depicted as the orange tree in full bloom.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/SD_tree_wFades3_002_02_200.jpg" width="550" height="356" alt="A graphic depiction of the “Self-Determination Model” with the overall graphic faded back except for the orange Be Proactive area in the upper middle. Bulleted list below Be Proactive: Take appropriate risks; Gain support and resources; Communicate and negotiate; Cope with criticism; Be determined." /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
